    "Long or multidocument tasks must still fit practical LM context windows.",
    "For specialized tasks (e.g., advanced numeric forecasting from documents), we will extend our work in the future.",
    "We identify multiple frontier scenarios-reasoning-based tasks (mathematical or causal), decision-making (market forecasts), advanced knowledge (fact completion, cross-lingual QA), and more (Liang et al., 2022).",
